Ghanian music act, Sarkodie is one of Ghana and indeed Africa’s most respected music acts and he has just proven that he deserves everything good written about him. Proving that he still got what it takes to remain atop his game, the award-winning has released a 3-minute long freestyle which he titles “My Advice” and it boasts of really dope lines. The Sarkcess Music frontman, in the freestyle, throws heavy shots reportedly aimed at fellow Ghanian artiste, Shatta Wale. The visual for the video is directed by Derrick. Hit the play button below and share your thoughts. 